snippet.title: MOUSE MAZE TRAILER | Movement Jam 2022 Submission
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for my submission to Movement Jam 2022 on itch.io! Play it now and let me know what you think!

Mouse Maze: https://fletchmakesstuff.itch.io/mouse-maze
Recorded with OBS: https://obsproject.com/
Edited with DaVinci Resolve 17: https://www.blackmagicdesign.com/products/davinciresolve
Thumbnail edited with GIMP: https://www.gimp.org/ 

Music: "Moose" from https://bensound.com/royalty-free-music
